Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.20,0:01:31.23,OPCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}我还是一如既往
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.35,0:01:37.56,OPCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}倘若能彼此交心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.96,0:01:45.90,OPCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}自那天起 四季更替时光流转
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.04,0:01:51.69,OPCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}我只想说 谢谢你伴我至今
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.08,0:01:59.90,OPCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}呵着白气 朝向狭窄的小巷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.03,0:02:05.29,OPCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}你温暖的手使劲拉着我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.39,0:02:07.25,OPCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}不断前行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.33,0:02:10.45,OPCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}好想马上就亲吻你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.70,0:02:14.15,OPCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}躲在自动售货机背后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.41,0:02:17.60,OPCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}害羞地凝视对方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.84,0:02:23.04,OPCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}温柔的心情洋溢胸口
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.30,0:02:26.57,OPCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}你还是一如既往
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.74,0:02:30.02,OPCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}我还是一如既往
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.36,0:02:35.46,OPCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}倘若能彼此交心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.58,0:02:37.61,OPCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}我们便能融为一体
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.69,0:02:40.81,OPCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}与一份小小幸福的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.08,0:02:44.36,OPCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}似乎就在触手可及的前方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.56,0:02:47.09,OPCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}能变得如此温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.12,0:02:50.05,OPCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}全因有你
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------EDCN5-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.87,0:24:33.92,EDCN6,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}无论是睡是醒 都如此眷恋
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.19,0:24:38.64,EDCN6,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}一直都注视着你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.54,0:24:44.64,EDCN6,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}无论欢欣的傍晚
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.88,0:24:49.32,EDCN6,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}还是消沉的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.51,0:24:55.40,EDCN6,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}你的肩膀总是那样温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.57,0:25:01.07,EDCN6,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}胸口好闷…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.89,0:25:06.18,EDCN6,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}快抱紧我
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.26,0:25:13.37,EDCN6,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}比任何人都要喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.55,0:25:19.34,EDCN6,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}平安夜那天 结为伴侣
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.54,0:25:25.98,EDCN6,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}喜欢你的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.12,0:25:30.47,EDCN6,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}直到永远
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------PREV-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.88,0:00:03.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.86,0:00:05.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.14,0:00:07.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这封情书是你寄的？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.82,0:00:09.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.54,0:00:12.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能给我一个答复么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.34,0:00:15.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是好的答复就更好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.60,0:00:19.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不了解你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.38,0:00:21.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前在什么地方见过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.80,0:00:24.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有…选我真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.76,0:00:26.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.25,0:00:28.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非你不可
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.69,0:00:30.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我喜欢你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.41,0:00:33.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不够格吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.86,0:00:34.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.96,0:00:36.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能和你这么可爱的女生交往
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.98,0:00:38.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.38,0:00:42.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪有…那么可爱…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.18,0:00:43.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.17,0:00:46.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果…不嫌弃我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.11,0:00:52.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.74,0:00:55.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好开心 太开心了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.60,0:00:57.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心意能传达给你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.00,0:00:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.43,0:01:02.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 2年B班的上崎里沙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.61,0:01:06.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从今天起就是橘纯一的女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.87,0:01:10.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能让你开心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.95,0:01:12.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么都愿意做
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------TXTA-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.35,0:02:56.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好期待响的杂烩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.28,0:03:03.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.41,0:03:04.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经到时间了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.04,0:03:06.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.19,0:03:09.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天午休能再来这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.81,0:03:11.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时再继续吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.98,0:03:13.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.56,0:03:16.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天中午能跟里沙继续今天的事
