Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.00,0:03:20.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.00,0:03:22.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.75,0:03:24.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美也 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.88,0:03:30.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 那个…女…女……女朋…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.01,0:03:32.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 老哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.36,0:03:34.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 没什么 我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.85,0:03:37.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪的老哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.65,0:03:39.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 尽管一直这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.40,0:03:43.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神崎里沙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.76,0:03:48.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个可爱的女孩啊 我的女朋友
